Malaysian authorities seized a second Chinese trawler poaching endangered turtles and other marine animals from waters off its coast this week ,.
A rare turtle has hatched at the Tennessee Aquarium, aquarium officials announced.
An Indonesian court is to try 23 Chinese men seized off the coast of Borneo trying to smuggle hundreds of endangered turtles, killed and stuffed to be sold as souvenirs ,.
They hatched a rare Arakan forest turtle this week, marking the fourth of the brown - and - tan spotted reptiles to be born.
